{
  "id": "RAW_36a810d4",
  "title": "90 后正在掌管中国 AI，凭实力活成了「爽文」主角",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247624503&idx=3&sn=90dee2fda0d9fa58a827eb80e739f8f7",
  "date": "2026-01-20 02:33:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mpa-action-id=\"mklwgqeglah\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51itw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">清华姚班、普林斯顿博士、前 OpenAI 核心成员、27 岁、首席 AI 科学家……当这些标签堆砌在一个人身上时，你很难不感受到一种来自智商层面的压迫感。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5161a\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但就是这种类似的标签组合，正在中国 AI 赛道上频繁出现。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51b8b\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">置身于 2026 年回望，在中国 AI 过去三年的狂飙突进中，昔日叱咤风云的互联网大佬似乎已退居幕后；取而代之站在舞台中央，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">是以梁文锋、姚顺雨、林俊旸、杨植麟为代表的 80 后乃至 90 后。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"AGI-Next 峰会圆桌实录，汇集了智谱AI 唐杰、腾讯姚顺雨、阿里林俊旸及杨强教授等领军人物的深度洞察。 指出中国大模型已进入分化时刻：从对\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593935\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9071a2df&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPdtzZPJa1qXxtNOMsic3as7dEAKkOXJECY4yyjgVsfibomOtDclFjnmzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <div style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwh29q7mr\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mklwh29v1d27\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">A</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwh29q7mr\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mklwh29v1d27\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">GI-Nex</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwh29q7mr\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mklwh29v1d27\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">t 峰会</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5tqx\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们之中，有人仰望星空，有人极致务实，甚至无意遵循上一代巨头立下的江湖规矩，却殊途同归地站在了 AGI 的大门口。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5rof\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与此同时，他们既有硬刚海外 AI 巨头的硬气，也不乏算力捉襟见肘时的窘迫。风浪极大，舵手极年轻，但这种反差，恰恰将是 2026 年中国 AI 最真实的切面：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:12px;padding:24px 15px 8px;color:rgb(105, 105, 105);font-size:14px;line-height:28px;margin-bottom:46px;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51ya6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">姚顺雨（1998 年）：腾讯 CEO/总裁办公室首席 AI 科学家</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5oel\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">林俊旸（1993 年）：通义千问系列模型研发主导者、阿里 P10</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5t9b\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">杨植麟（1992 年）：月之暗面创始人</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51ipf\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">罗福莉（1995 年）： 小米 MiMo 大模型负责人</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51hmp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">梁文锋（1985 年）：DeepSeek 创始人</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe518ck\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">闫俊杰（1989 年）：MiniMax 创始人</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5n12\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">张鹏（1980 年）：智谱 AI 创始人</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5202s\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">张祥雨（1990 年）：阶跃星辰首席科学家</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51n03\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">……</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">80/90 后，站在了 AGI 的大门口</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:0px 0px 27px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5g0o\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">风险投资公司 Antler 曾公布一项数据：2024 年，AI 独角兽创始人的平均年龄已经降到了 29 岁，而其他行业还在 34 岁徘徊。甚至像 Mercor 这样的百亿美元估值公司，三位创始人今年才刚满 22 岁。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51k7k\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">视线转回国内，这种「低龄化」情况屡见不鲜。大象虽然转身慢，但巨头们做了一个极其聪明的决定：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">既然打不过年轻人，那就把年轻人变成自己人。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51i6v\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，腾讯选择了 27 岁的姚顺雨。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51w5d\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1998 年出生，清华姚班，普林斯顿博士，前 OpenAI 核心成员，专注于「让 AI 像人一样思考和行动」的课题。他提出的 ReAct 框架和（Tree of Thoughts）决策框架，被业内奉为 AI Agent 的教科书级理论。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe518ko\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2025 年，腾讯直接将其招致麾下，任命为「CEO/总裁办公室首席 AI 科学家」的头衔，也将 AI Infra 和大模型研究的重任交给这位 95 后。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"腾讯引入27岁前OpenAI研究员姚顺雨担任AI负责人\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593932\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"840\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=229ebd32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPibcNsVicV0ojvuibV1zhUvp6UuLkwICAeQCVJGJy2spygRmDEWygCByOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 15px;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(167, 167, 167); text-align: center; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 2 [\\&quot;para\\&quot;,{\\&quot;tagName\\&quot;:\\&quot;section\\&quot;,\\&quot;attributes\\&quot;:{\\&quot;style\\&quot;:\\&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\\\\\&quot;Segoe UI\\\\\\&quot;, Roboto, \\\\\\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\\\\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\\&quot;,\\&quot;data-pm-slice\\&quot;:\\&quot;0 0 []\\&quot;},\\&quot;namespaceURI\\&quot;:\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\&quot;},\\&quot;para\\&quot;,{\\&quot;tagName\\&quot;:\\&quot;section\\&quot;,\\&quot;attributes\\&quot;:{},\\&quot;namespaceURI\\&quot;:\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\&quot;}]&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwizu8fod\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mklwizub8ao\">姚顺雨</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51quq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在最近的 AGI-Next 峰会上，我们也能看出姚顺雨对于 ToC 和 ToB 的大模型路径均有深刻见解：他指出 ToC 要依赖「上下文」提供情绪价值，而 ToB 比拼「生产力」，企业只愿为最强模型付费 。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51ho2\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他强调在 ToC 侧充分利用微信等生态的海量上下文，在 ToB 侧发挥大公司真实场景和数据优势，以此破局 AI 应用。这不仅仅是技术路线的选择，更是在为腾讯庞大的社交生态寻找 AI 时代的出口。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5gsc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">同样打破大厂晋升纪录的，还有阿里的林俊旸。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5ssk\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1993 年的北大才子，在阿里达摩院一路狂飙，2025 年，32 岁的他成了阿里史上最年轻的 P10。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"今天，唐杰、杨植麟、林俊旸、姚顺雨同台交锋！聊透了2026年AI的重点- 知乎\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593915\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7fdf54de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPj82UhUhsRKEfOcCXQh20CvYwOKnldEIuTgFhvNVDbsIWW5tGtADkxA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0;padding: 0 15px;font-size: 15px;color: #222222;text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe59ok\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">林俊旸</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5b0t\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他曾参与研发阿里达摩院的千亿参数多模态模型 M6，主导通义千问系列模型研发，涵盖多模态、模型优化训练、代码生成、数学推理等领域。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe513mk\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">作为通义千问（Qwen）开源策略的一手推动者，他不仅在全球开发者社区撕开了一道口子，更让阿里在激烈的模型竞赛中稳住了身位。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5z42\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果说巨头内部的年轻化是由于生存焦虑，那么 AI 创业战场上的厮杀，则更多了几分个人英雄主义的色彩。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">月之暗面的杨植麟大概是这个群体里最像拿到爽文男主剧本的那一个。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"GPT革命｜月之暗面杨植麟：Kimi月均活跃用户3600万多模态模型在内测\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593916\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"840\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18f004de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPpgIa6qadwr0W2kS1r14RicSibEaxR1cm50MIOhicFJBjM3EFmWiav1fJxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51t8e\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">杨植麟</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5mbv\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1992 年出生，清华学霸，卡内基梅隆博士，2019 年提出 XLNet 模型的作者之一，这位理工男有着特有的浪漫，所创立的公司命名为「月之暗面」，源自 Pink Floyd 的专辑。在多次公开场合的露面中，他也热衷于讨论 AGI 理念，在信奉 Scaling Law 的道路上无比坚决。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5o1w\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">而在光谱的另一端，梁文锋则是另一种画风。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51mo7\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然同样都是名牌大学出身，本科就读于浙江大学电子信息工程专业，硕士继续在浙大信息与通信工程专业深造，但背靠量化私募巨头幻方量化，DeepSeek 自带一股「带资进组」的硬气。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5bbf\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">去年，幻方量化以 56.6% 的平均回报率跻身中国百亿级量化基金业绩榜第二，仅次于宁波灵均投资 70% 多的收益率，也为 DeepSeek 的发展填上了更充足的弹药。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"刚刚，DeepSeek梁文锋入选Nature年度十大人物！被称为「科技颠覆者」\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/ePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPh3yxj5L78Up4BE5yMyO5q833955rTyiaPXP7ibA7NsKufCAZ8H4zZMdw/0?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1072.1167883211679\" data-cropy2=\"599.1240875912409\" data-imgfileid=\"503593917\" data-ratio=\"0.558768656716418\" style=\"width: 544px;height: 304px;background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1072\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8d7cae3a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPqX8ypAZGOapSdXRFb4ibibzWXrptjQPdDfoFMDYcZSgFwX9kRc4nqKOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0;padding: 0 15px;font-size: 15px;color: #222222;text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5ikn\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">梁文锋</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5zc4\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从 2024 年 5 月的 DeepSeek-V2 开始，他们持续迭代并开源了 236B→671B 的 DeepSeekMoE 系列，在国内最早系统地把「细粒度专家分割 + 共享专家隔离 + 无辅助损失负载均衡」等想法写进论文、放出了完整权重。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51rbr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">此外，得益于在 AI Infra 等方面的持续优化， DeepSeek 硬是靠着这种在螺蛳壳里做道场的本事，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用有限的算力打造了 DeepSeek V3 和 R1 这样极具破坏力的产品。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5uel\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当 DeepSeek 以极低的 API 价格血洗市场时，所有的 AI 模型创业者都感到了一阵寒意。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe57s9\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至大模型 Xiaomi MiMo 的负责人罗福莉同样出自 DeepSeek，2022 年加入幻方量化，负责深度学习策略建模；也是 MoE 大模型 DeepSeek-V2 的核心开发者之一 。去年 11 月 12 日，她正式官宣加入小米，负责推进小米 AGI 方向的研发落地。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"AI天才少女罗福莉首次公开亮相并登台发表演讲-快科技-科技改变生活\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593919\" data-ratio=\"0.574146614437605\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1787\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4fdd6b5b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPvPpeglddDCW7y1KfgobXlyrjqJH8E07ze6hCOuBVO8zUTTLRTNCpAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5gr3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Leonis AI 100 报告显示，大多数 AI 创始人在创业时只有 20 多岁。Antler 的数据更惊人：AI 公司从成立到成为独角兽，平均只需要 4.7 年，比其他行业快了整整两年。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5ol7\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">MiniMax 和智谱就是这种「中国速度」的代表。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5r70\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">技术的尽头是商业化，1 月 9 日，MiniMax 在港股敲钟，市值一度冲破千亿，从创立到上市只用了 4 年。MiniMax 共计员工 385 人，但团队平均年龄 29 岁，人均 95 后，385 个人里 73.8% 是研发，三分之一有海外背景。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"我所知道的闫俊杰| 学习AIGC\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593920\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83281e70&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPnAIGC4C1y6GZ5oeOJmkicvELC5PMg5NQj9eDhVwgzDSv6wBluLvxxoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5rk3\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">闫俊杰</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe523dy\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">创始人闫俊杰在 2015 年毕业于中科院自动化所获博士，此后在清华计算机系做博士后研究，曾任商汤科技副总裁、研究院副院长兼智慧城市 CTO。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5zr5\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了闫俊杰，MiniMax 还有多位年轻核心人物：贠烨祎（31 岁，COO，前商汤战略负责人）、赵鹏宇（29 岁，大语言模型负责人）和周彧聪（32 岁，联合创始人兼视觉多模态负责人）等等。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51w88\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">以及清华系的智谱 AI，唐杰教授坐镇，80 后 CEO 张鹏冲锋，是学术圈与年轻团队结合的典型代表。</span>这家公司在 2026 年初抢了 MiniMax 的风头，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">成为全球「大模型第一股」，市值一度逼近 800 亿港元。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"张鹏| 2024全球机器学习技术大会\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593921\" data-ratio=\"0.6386054421768708\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1176\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17a41c83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPTYQHL2ST20w3tA4wVgzM7fDUmZZEUzvFibRh1H4fY5peznp0Vro9Gog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0;padding: 0 15px;font-size: 15px;color: #222222;text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51m8w\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(167, 167, 167);text-align: center;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">张鹏</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe513cq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有前微软全球副总裁姜大昕创立的阶跃星辰，核心团队全是 90 后，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">首席科学家张祥雨作为 ResNet 残差网络论文的作者之一蜚声学术界，</span>同样也是 90 后 AI 新星，其论文总引用数超过 30 万次。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51e9c\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无论互联网巨头内部，还是新兴独角兽企业中，35 岁以下的技术领袖已经全面崛起。他们正走上核心岗位，掌握着关键决策和研发方向，成为中国 AI 大模型竞赛的主力军。</span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">名校+竞赛+顶级机构历练，成了中国 AI 领军人物的三件套</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:0px 0px 27px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51csi\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上一代互联网巨头的创始人多为 60 后、70 后，对比之下，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这一波 AI 浪潮的领导者整体年龄提前了至少 20 岁。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe519kq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">究其原因，AI 是一个知识迭代极快的新兴领域，需要颠覆性思维和快速学习能力，天然青睐年轻头脑 。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5oh3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Transformer 架构提出不到 10 年，ChatGPT 爆发才 3 年。在 LLM（大语言模型）这个领域，大家的起跑线其实相差无几。甚至年轻人因为没有「思维包袱」，反而更容易接受 Scaling Law 的暴力美学。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Scaling Laws — LessWrong\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593922\" data-ratio=\"0.3037037037037037\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5114bc9e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPA1VPicgbaBtp6IgD1ibzNicYLF8EEPdBSqfPxCbdFqq1cjOH8ia0OoG55w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51b1j\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">此外，教育的伏笔其实早已埋下，中国在 2000 年前后启动的大批英才教育计划（如清华「姚班」等）如今开始结出硕果。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5rsw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">姚顺雨获 NOI 银牌，杨植麟获信息学奥赛省一等奖。这些经历培养了他们优秀的算法和编码能力，也让他们更早接触高水平的计算机科学训练。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5305\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">凭借在竞赛中脱颖而出，他们当中也有不少人保送进入清华、北大等名校计算机相关专业 。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5el2\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从学历背景来看，姚顺雨、杨植麟、张鹏均为清华系，闫俊杰在清华做博士后。其他人也多来自北大、浙大、上交大、北航等一流院校。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51v95\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些名校背景帮助他们打下了扎实的理论基础和视野，当 AI 迎来创业风口，这批人顺理成章地成为主角。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593926\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bbe99167&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPQ7BKbKnJsP7n9X1TvOicQVicD6nUleZuGA5FibQKUVkPLvJYewHqGWynw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5jgo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更重要的是周期的更替。上一轮移动互联网的红利已经见顶。大模型的范式转移，为年轻人提供了一个巨大的超车机会。资本也乐于寻找新故事，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这让年轻创业者获得了超越资历的资源支持。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5139m\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，一些专家学者指出，90 后、95 后创业者相较前辈更敢想敢干、也更强调自我价值实现。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe553k\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如在最近的 AGI-Next 峰会上，唐杰教授评价说：90 后、00 后更具冒险精神，要为敢冒险的年轻一代提供更好的创新环境 。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">相应地，这一代创业者很多不满足于在大厂按部就班升职，而是渴望掌舵核心项目或自主创业。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"唐杰、杨强、杨植麟、林俊旸和刚回国的姚顺雨坐一起都聊了啥？ - 知乎\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593924\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44405b13&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwPqHoVkfuqiaDB9ueiaWCtQmRZBETI4bQLiaf8LXP4nLeXrJuE9l26icE7hg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe512tl\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这种内在驱动力，使他们在机会来临时果断走向台前，同时年轻一代普遍国际化视野更开阔，不少人有海外留学或工作经历（姚顺雨、杨植麟等），更能直接对标 OpenAI、DeepMind 等全球标杆，怀抱实现「中国版 OpenAI」的使命感。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5wdq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">基于此，中国 AI 创业者年轻化并非偶然：既有 AI 技术迭代特性的必然要求，又有教育体系和环境支持的厚积薄发，更有年轻一代勇于冒险、不拘一格的精神使然。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe511p3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">国际化技术视野、大规模工程实践经验、顶尖人脉资源，顶级机构的背书也都为他们独当一面打下坚实基础。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503593930\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2c8f494&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPiaJ52ZO7aRr0rmukG9ZLwP9HePQmKxzYhMc0H86UmawHYIDDxdQSrhXfF5asPPDZPTfvcYdmfeicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51jkd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然而，年轻并非免死金牌，现实也远比外界想象更为粗砺。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe56a7\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一方面，OpenAI 与 Google 在模型推理能力与多模态交互上构筑的技术壁垒，仍在以月为单位不断抬升；</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51xbc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另一方面，如何在算力资源并不富裕的客观条件下，通过架构创新与工程优化，榨干每一块芯片的极限性能，成了摆在每一位年轻舵手面前必须直面的技术大考。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe5vzr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">而在技术之外，商业模式的模糊性依然悬在头顶。尽管应用层百花齐放，但在高企的训练与推理成本面前，如何找到可持续的造血机制，依然是全行业都在摸着石头过河的难题。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51wsd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">风浪确实大，但这恰恰是年轻人的主场。他们还有时间去试错，去推倒重来。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 15px;margin:27px 0px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mklwgqe51huw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">在 AI 这个方兴未艾、快速迭代的领域，既没有论资排辈的规则，也没有巨人的肩膀可以依靠。但这反倒成了一种自由——不用循规蹈矩，不用致敬前浪，他们走到哪，哪里就是路。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文首发于公众号「APPSO」（ID：appsolution），这是一个让你手机更好用的专业媒体，欢迎点击下方卡片进行关注。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度盘点了中国 AI 领域 80/90 后技术领袖的崛起现状，分析了名校背景、竞赛经历与顶级机构历练如何塑造这批 AGI 时代的年轻舵手。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度盘点了中国 AI 领域 80/90 后技术领袖的崛起现状，分析了名校背景、竞赛经历与顶级机构历练如何塑造这批 AGI 时代的年轻舵手。",
  "summary": "文章聚焦于 2026 年中国 AI 赛道的权力更迭，指出以姚顺雨、林俊旸、杨植麟、梁文锋等为代表的 80 后、90 后已全面接管大模型研发与决策核心。文章详细梳理了这些领军人物的背景：他们大多拥有清华姚班、名校博士等顶尖学历，具备 NOI 等竞赛获奖经历，并曾在 OpenAI、微软等顶级机构历练。分析认为，AI 技术的极速迭代、英才教育计划的厚积薄发以及移动互联网红利见顶后的范式转移，共同促成了这一人才“低龄化”现象。尽管面临技术壁垒、算力限制和商业模式模糊等挑战，这群年轻领袖正凭借无思维包袱的创新精神和国际化视野，在巨头内部或自主创业战场上，努力打造中国版的 AGI 未来。",
